These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre        | crime   | fantasy   |
| Hobby   | fishing | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, lilac
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, montecristo
1. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Color   | lilac | purple   |
| Cigar      | montecristo | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
