.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-8::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, mouse
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, april
1. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |
| Pet         | mouse | fish |
| Birthday   | june   | april   |

